nodes.text: Star Wars Helmet Collection 39 is the thirty-ninth issue of Star Wars Helmet Collection, published by De Agostini. The issue includes a 1:5 scale replica of Zam Wesell's helmet.
The issue states that Zam Wesell spoke Huttese in her final moments, when the language she spoke was actually identified as Clawdite in Star Wars By the Numbers.
